s''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制作步骤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">准备好新鲜的豆腐一块。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">香椿芽洗净。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">豆腐切成小丁。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">把豆腐放入开水锅内焯水捞出过凉水。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">再把香椿芽放入锅内烫至变色捞出放入冷水中降温。</sp