mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">倒入切好的鸡丁一起翻炒</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">炒到鸡丁变色，放入料酒</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">6&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">放入适量的老抽</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">7&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">加入适量的盐</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">8&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">加入适量的糖</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">9&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">加入适量的味精</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">10&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">翻炒到鸡肉断生即可出锅装盘</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">小贴士</span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">辣椒看自己喜好，不喜欢吃辣的可以少放</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->', 'images/201409/thumb_img/40_thumb_G_1411706779758.jpg', 'images/201409/goods_img/40_G_1411706779835.jpg', 'images/201409/source_img/40_G_1411706779079.JPG', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1411706779, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1412811224, 10, '', -1, -1, 0, NULL, 12, 0, '', ''),
(43, 28, '10069', '小汤山水泡青豆 无公害蔬菜200g', '+', 4, 12, '', 100, '0.200', '9.00', '8.00', 0, 0, '0.00', 0, 0, 10, '', '', '<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品名称】青豆</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品品牌】小汤山</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品等级】无公害</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品规格】</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">200~200g/</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">份</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品介绍】</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">为豆科大豆属一年生草本植物，原产中国。中国自古栽培，已有</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5000</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">年的种植史。在中国普遍种植，在东北、华北、陕、川及长江下游地区均有出产，以长江流域及西南栽培较多，以东北大豆质量最优。世界各国栽培的大豆都是直接或间接由中国传播的。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、青豆富含不饱和脂肪酸和大豆磷脂，有保持血管弹性、健脑和防止脂肪肝形成的作用；</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、青豆中富含皂角苷、蛋白酶抑制剂、异黄酮、钼、硒等抗癌成分，对前列腺癌、皮肤癌、肠癌、食道癌等几乎所有的癌症都有抑制作用。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、青豆除了含有蛋白质和纤维，它也是人体摄取维生素</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">A</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、维生素</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">C</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">和维生素</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">K</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，以及维生素</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">B</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的重要来源食物之一。青豆还能提供少量钙，磷，钾，铁，硫胺素和核黄素。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">酥脯青豆</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食材</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">200g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">青豆</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">配料适量油</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量盐</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量菜脯</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量猪肉</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制作步骤</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">备青豆，猪肉，菜脯。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">热锅加油，下肉片及菜脯丁。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">炒至菜脯丁出香后，加入青豆同炒。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">炒至青豆出香，变色后。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">加入适量细盐。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">6&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">加入适量清水微焖至豆熟。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">7&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一份酥菜青豆就完成了。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">小贴士</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">在炒制的时候，注意火候，可加入适量清水。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->', 'images/201409/thumb_img/43_thumb_G_1411707495230.jpg', 'images/201409/goods_img/43_G_1411707495024.jpg', 'images/201409/source_img/43_G_1411707495012.JPG', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1411707495, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1412811236, 0, '', -1, -1, 0, NULL, 12, 0, '', ''),
