ont-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">又名不结球白菜、青菜、油菜。原产于我国，南北各地均有分布，在我国栽培十分广泛。据测定，小白菜是蔬菜中含矿物质和维生素最丰富的菜。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">小白菜为含维生素和矿物质最丰富的蔬菜之一，为保证身体的生理需要提供物质条件，有助于增强机体免疫能力。小白菜中含有大量粗纤维，其进入人体内与脂肪结合后，可防止血浆胆固醇形成，促使胆固醇代谢物胆酸得以排出体外，以减少动脉粥样硬化的形成，从而保持血管弹性。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: ''yes''">小白菜炖豆腐</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食材</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">300g</span><spa