e: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">球生菜（又称西生菜、圆生菜）为菊科莴苣属</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;1&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">或</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;2&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">年生草本植物半结球莴苣或结球莴苣。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">生菜有清肝利胆和养胃的功效。纤维和维生素</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">C</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">较白菜多，有消除多余脂肪的作用，故又叫减肥生菜。因其茎叶中含有莴苣素，故味微苦，具有镇痛催眠、降低胆固醇、辅助治疗神经衰弱等功效。生菜中含有甘露醇等有效成分，有利尿和促进血液循环的作用。性质甘凉，有清热爽神之功效。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: ''yes''">生菜鸡蛋汤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食材</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">50g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">生菜</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">配料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">个鸡蛋</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;1</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">根火腿肠</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量盐</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量香油</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制作步骤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">鸡蛋打散。火腿肠切片，生菜切丝备用。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" styl