n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">番杏，又名海滨篙苣，为番杏科多年生草本。生于海滨盐碱沙地，或栽培于园圃，茎高</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2~3</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">尺，叶有柄，质厚而软，茎叶多带肉质，嫩叶供食用，中国台湾、福建、浙江宁波等地均有分布，全草入药。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">番杏具有清热、解毒、利尿消肿等作用，常食番杏对于肠炎、胃癌、食道癌、直肠癌、败血病、肾病等患者具有较好的缓解病痛的作用。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: ''yes''">凉拌番杏叶</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食材</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料番杏叶</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">配料生抽</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">少许醋</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">盐</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">鸡精</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">蒜末</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制作步骤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">番杏叶去掉老杆后清洗干净。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2&nbsp;