'Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食材</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">500g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">穿心莲</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;200g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">腰果</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;20g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">红彩椒</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">配料适量蒜末</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量橄榄油</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量盐</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量糖</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量醋</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量香油</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制作步骤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">新鲜穿心莲一斤左右，放入盆中冲洗干净</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">热锅凉油，下入腰果，小火翻炒</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">腰果呈浅金黄色并炒出香味后，立刻关火，盛出晾凉</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">把洗干净的穿心莲放入开水中快速焯水，盛出后过冷水保持菜的本色</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">准备好适量蒜末和少许红彩椒碎丁，把橄榄油、盐、糖、醋调至成汁<