ize: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">花椰菜（学名：</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Brassica&nbsp;oleracea&nbsp;L.&nbsp;var.&nbsp;botrytis&nbsp;L.</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">），是一种蔬菜。为十字花科芸薹属一年生植物，与西兰花（青花菜）和结球甘蓝同为甘蓝的变种。原产于地中海东部海岸，约在</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">19</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">世纪初</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">清光绪年间引进中国。又名花菜、椰花菜、甘蓝花、洋花菜、球花甘蓝。有白、绿两种，绿色的叫西蓝花、青花菜。白花菜和绿花菜的营养、作用基本相同，绿花菜比白花菜的胡萝卜素含量要高些。在《时代》杂志推荐的十大健康食品中名列第四。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">是一种粗纤维含量少，品质鲜嫩，营养丰富，风味鲜美，人们喜食的蔬菜。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: ''yes''">干煸菜花</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.