font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">金针菇学名毛柄金钱菌，又称毛柄小火菇、构菌、朴菇、冬菇、朴菰</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、冻菌、金菇、智力菇等，英文为：&ldquo;</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Enoki&nbsp;Mushroom</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&rdquo;，植物学名为</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Flammulina&nbsp;velutiper&nbsp;(Fr.)&nbsp;Sing</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">。因其菌柄细长，似金针菜，故称金针菇，属伞菌目白蘑科金针菇属，是一种菌藻地衣类。金针菇具有很高的药用食疗作用。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">金针菇不仅味道鲜美，而且营养丰富，是拌凉菜和火锅食品的原料之一。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">葱油拌金针菇</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食材</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">180g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">金针菇</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;30g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">胡萝卜</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;50g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">黄瓜</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">配料</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4ml</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">生抽</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;10ml</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">陈醋</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;2g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">食用盐</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;5g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">蜂蜜</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;30g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">熟芝麻</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适量小葱</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制作步骤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">原料：金针菇，胡萝卜，黄瓜，小葱。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">味汁：醋，生抽，盐，蜂蜜，熟芝麻。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">黄瓜，胡萝卜各切成丝状，金针菇去掉根部，小葱切小段。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">锅内加入清水放适量盐，水沸腾后倒入金针菇。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">烫</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">10</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">秒立即捞出过冷水。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">金针菇沥干水分排在盘子中，加入黄瓜丝备用。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">锅内放油，（最好不要放香味很浓的油，不然会掩盖葱油本身的味道了），加入葱段。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">6&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">中火慢熬至颜色微黄，转小火熬到焦香，捞出葱叶滤油，也可以直接全部捞出。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">7&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">锅内用底油炒香胡萝卜，炒香后捞出摆在金针菇上面。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">8&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">调入味汁和葱油搅拌入味即可食用。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">小贴士</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">葱油一次可以多做一些，待凉后放在干爽的玻璃瓶里冷藏保存，不过我觉得还是现做比较好，香味犹存。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->', 'images/201409/thumb_img/75_thumb_G_1411770403064.jpg', 'images/201409/goods_img/75_G_1411770403442.jpg', 'images/201409/source_img/75_G_1411770403333.JPG', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1411770403, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1412810949, 0, '', -1, -1, 0, NULL, 12, 0, '', ''),
(76, 29, '10104', '小汤山 散白菜花 无公害蔬菜200g', '+', 12, 12, '', 100, '0.200', '11.00', '9.60', 0, 0, '0.00', 0, 0, 10, '', '', '<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品名称】菜花</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品品牌】小汤山</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品等级】无公害</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品规格】</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">200</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">g</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">/</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">份</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【储存方法】置于阴凉干燥处，并尽快食用。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【产品介绍】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">花椰菜（学名：</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Brassica&nbsp;oleracea&nbsp;L.&nbsp;var.&nbsp;botrytis&nbsp;L.</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">），是一种蔬菜。为十字花科芸薹属一年生植物，与西兰花（青花菜）和结球甘蓝同为甘蓝的变种。原产于地中海东部海岸，约在</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">19</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">世纪初</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">清光绪年间引进中国。又名花菜、椰花菜、甘蓝花、洋花菜、球花甘蓝。有白、绿两种，绿色的叫西蓝花、青花菜。白花菜和绿花菜的营养、作用基本相同，绿花菜比白花菜的胡萝卜素含量要高些。在《时代》杂志推荐的十大健康食品中名列第四。</span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【营养价值】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">是一种粗纤维含量少，品质鲜嫩，营养丰富，风味鲜美，人们喜食的蔬菜。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【食谱推荐】</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: ''yes''">素炒散头菜花</span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主料散头菜花<font face="Calibri">400g&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">辅料油适量盐适量生抽适量蒜粒少许</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">步骤</span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1.<font face="宋体">散头菜花洗净。</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2.<font face="宋体">择成小朵然后焯水。</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3.<font face="宋体">捞出后立马过冷水。</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4.<font face="宋体">锅中放油加入蒜粒炒香。</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5.<font face="宋体">放入菜花炒一分钟。</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">6.<font face="宋体">加入生抽及盐调味即可。</font></span></span><span style="font-family: ''Calibri''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->', 'images/201409/thumb_img/76_thumb_G_1411770494432.jpg', 'images/201409/goods_img/76_G_1411770494059.jpg', 'images/201409/source_img/76_G_1411770494674.JPG', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1411770494, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1412810953, 0, '', -1, -1, 0, NULL, 12, 0, '', '');
